Subject: Netsoc account created

You've successfully set up your new Netsoc account.
Please email support@netsoc.tcd.ie if you lose your password 
or have any difficulties using the netsoc servers.

You can log into IRC and chat with the rest of Netsoc by
using SSH to "login.netsoc.tcd.ie" and running "chat"
(download Putty from http://netsoc.tcd.ie if you're on
Windows).

For information about how to use Netsoc services, visit
the Wiki at http://wiki.netsoc.tcd.ie.

Thanks for joining Netsoc!

Netsoc Support

